## Summary
This documentation page explains how to create and interpret recommendations in Amplitude Activation, detailing the three types (Top Trending, Most Popular, and AI Based), the step-by-step process for building each type, how to define outcomes and item catalogs, and how to analyze recommendation performance metrics including confidence scores and lift measurements.

